Case No. 1,059. In re BARRY. [Cited in Bennett v. Bennett, Case No. 1,318.]

[The case reported under this title in Brun-ner, Col. Cas, 533, 7 Law Rep. 374, 11 Hunt, Her. Mag. 265. and 136 U. S. 597, note, is the same as In re Barry, 42 Fed. 113. The decision was affirmed in 5 How. (46 U. S.) 103.]
